OL,3,CWarning over printing equipment linked
OL,4,Cto factory blast
OL,6,FAn urgent safety warning has been
OL,7,Fissued to companies using printing
OL,8,Fmachinery linked to a devastating
OL,9,Fexplosion and fire on a Swindon
OL,10,Findustrial estate last month.
OL,12,FThe Health and Safety Executive (HSE)
OL,13,Fhas asked firms to check new guidance
OL,14,Fover the use of what is known as a
OL,15,FSublimation Calender Machine,
OL,16,Fmanufactured by Diferro.
