OL,3,CWarning over printing equipment linked
OL,4,Cto factory blast
OL,6,FThis machine was in use at a printing
OL,7,Ffirm on the Groundwell Industrial
OL,8,FEstate in Swindon where an explosion
OL,9,Fand subsequent fire destroyed the
OL,10,Fbuilding on 24 September.
OL,12,FIn a press release the HSE said it was
OL,13,Ftaking steps to stop any other Diferro
OL,14,Fmachines from coming into the country.
OL,16,FThe regulator added that anyone using
OL,17,Fthe equipment should not leave it
OL,18,Funattended while it is connected to
OL,19,Fthe power supply. If in any doubt, the
OL,20,FHSE said, the equipment shouldn't be
OL,21,Fused.
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G2/4
