OL,3,CWarning over printing equipment linked
OL,4,Cto factory blast
OL,6,FIt is also investigating the design of
OL,7,Fthe machine and a possible link with a
OL,8,Fsimilar explosion in South Wales in
OL,9,F2023, which led to a fatality.
OL,11,FLuke Messenger, head of technical
OL,12,Fproduct safety at the HSE, said: "We
OL,13,Fhave significant concerns about the
OL,14,Fsafe use of these machines.
OL,16,F"The guidance issued following the
OL,17,FTreforest Industrial Estate incident
OL,18,F(in South Wales) has clear
OL,19,Finstructions ` revisions to this have
OL,20,Fbeen published and we will continue to
OL,21,Fshare any further updates.
